name: Obsessions With Vert
description: A lot of my athletic efforts have in one way or another revolved around vertical meters. This audio-supported visualization uses my recent years of activity data and plots the cumulative vertical gain over its duration for each activity. Each single activity has its own starting point in the visualization and is located vertically close to the day of the year that the activity was performed in. The data preprocessing was done in Python, the visualization was designed in P5.js.
